uation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n <li>dla instancji obiektu <code>Boolean</code> metoda <code>toSource</code> zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący kod źródłowy.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Metoda ta jest zwykle stosowana wewnętrznie przez interpreter JavaScriptu, a nie bezpośrednio w kodzie programów.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toSource()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce"}],"summary":"Zwraca łańcuch znaków z kodem źródłowym obiektu.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Boolean.prototype.toSource()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Boolean.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Boolean.prototype.toSource()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Boolean.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Boolean.prototype.toSource()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/boolean/tostring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/boolean/tostring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"Boolean.prototype.toSource() | MDN","noIndexing":true}}